<!-- Contact Area Start -->
<div class="contact-area ptb-80">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <h1 class="page-title">RETURN POLICY</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <p>
                <strong>Terms and Conditions</strong><br>
                – Goods must be returned within 14 working days of purchase.<br>
                – Stocks returned later than 14 days will incur a minimum 10% handling fee.<br>
                – Goods must be returned in their original condition &amp; packaging ( i.e. all pins, clips, card boards clear plastic all intact). If not adhered to , a 10% handling fee will charged.<br>
                – Goods must be unsoiled ( i.e. No stains, marks, etc. )<br>
                – No&nbsp; returns will be accepted without a corresponding invoice.<br>
                – Garments not in their original condition will not be eligible for credit.<br>
                – Specialized or branded stock will definitely not be accepted for credit.<br>
                – Colmart has the right to decline a return.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
